### Variables
# CloudAMQP management API
# vhost: gtbvjenp (URL-encoded in path)

### Send hangout invite to userJan
POST https://seal.lmq.cloudamqp.com/api/exchanges/gtbvjenp/zuyp.notifications/publish
Authorization: Basic gtbvjenp LoRo_Eayh9R-k1zdq47nwpJa3vLUDj-t
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "properties": {},
  "routing_key": "user-20000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "payload": "{\"type\":\"hangout_invite\",\"hangoutId\":\"hangout-abc123\"}",
  "payload_encoding": "string"
}

